        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Exemptions for Critical Workers Act</b></p> <p>This bill exempts critical infrastructure workers from any federal mandate requiring federal employees or contractors to receive a COVID-19 vaccination. Critical infrastructure workers are identified in guidance from the Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Agency.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
